Thetis Reactor of University of Ghent.
.For the nuclides of interest high-purity compounds
efficiency 7.8%) or a Low Energy Photon Detector
(resolution 248 eV for the 5. 9 keV Fe X-ray);
volume 40 cm3) for Some long-lived radioisotopes
.The resonance integral (RI) was determined from the
cross section,CR = Cadmium ratio and R the ratio
of the thermal to epithermal neutron flux.
.The R were determined with gold monitor.
.The thermal cross sections were taken from the Chart
.In addition to the resonance integral are given the
half life of the produced isotope, the main gamma-
line, the thermal cross section, the ratio of res.
integral to thermal cross section, some  literature
values  for resonance integral and the main
.For thermal and epithermal self-shielding for the
